These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, marigold, tulip, begonia
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growslily##1
2. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##2
6. the person who growsbegonia is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Flower   | begonia | lily     | tulip | marigold |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, lemon, nectarine, cranberry
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, snowmobile, trike
1. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person eating nectarine is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Food   | corn | lemon    | cranberry     | nectarine  |
| Transport     | bus    | snowmobile | helicopter | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, pop, rock
House: colonial, gothic-revival, cottage, art-deco
1. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
3. the cottage house is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the colonial house is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
5. the cottage house is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | pop   | house  | rock |
| House           | gothic-revival | art-deco | cottage | colonial  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, rat, hedgehog, pony
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, egyptian, indian
1. the indian is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the turtle and the egyptian##2
3. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
6. the argentine is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Pet         | rat | turtle | pony | hedgehog  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine   | indian  | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla, goldfish, bird
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the owner of the bird is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk    |
| Pet      | chinchilla | mouse | goldfish       | bird |

