.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, plum, banana, strawberry
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person eating banana is between the person eating strawberry and the person drinking juice##2
3. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating banana and the person drinking coffee##2
4. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | coffee | juice | soy-milk | fanta |
| Food   | plum | grapefruit  | banana    | strawberry  |

