.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, french, indian, thai
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, engineer, entrepreneur, journalist
1. the journalist is on the right of the egyptian##1
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the engineer is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
4. the indian is between the french and the thai##2
5. the engineer is the engineer##1
6. the engineer is between the entrepreneur and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | egyptian | thai | indian | french     |
| Job     | firefighter | journalist  | engineer   | entrepreneur |

