.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, horse, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, motorbike, airplane
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the airplane is the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the fish is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | chinchilla | fish   | horse      | snake      |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | motorbike | bike | airplane |

