.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, jazz, salsa
4 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, guinea-pig, snake
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the fan of jazz is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the ferret##2
3. the fan of electronic is the owner of the ferret##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | classical | electronic | jazz      | salsa   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig  | ferret    | mouse | snake |

