.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, filmmaking, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, snowboarding, cycling, skateboarding
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | card-games | filmmaking | writing    | chess      |
| Sport   | cycling       | skateboarding       | snowboarding | parkour |

