.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, german, turkish
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, board-games, magic-tricks
1. the canadian is on the far right##1
2. the american is the american##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the german is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the turkish##3
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | american | german  | turkish | canadian |
| Hobby           | board-games     | magic-tricks | gardening    | puzzles     |

