.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-16::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, dunhill, prince, bongani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, parkour, rugby, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
2. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
3. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Cigar   | havana | bongani | prince | dunhill |
| Sport         | parkour  | rugby   | soccer | golf     |

